                    <lev2>
                        <title>MOUNTING</title>
                        <para>
                            <hotlnk xrefid="f0403801">The EC-17 controller is available in two different mounting
                                styles.
                            </hotlnk>
                            One model uses a stand-alone mounting design. It is intended for bracket mounting to a frame
                            member and is not attached to an antilock relay valve.
                        </para>
                        <para>The other EC-17 is designed to be mounted on one of four different valves. All of the
                            valves provide the relay function and replace the standard services relay on antilock
                            equipped vehicles. In some instances the valves also provide specialized functions. When the
                            EC-17 is mounted on any of these valves, the result is a
                            <hotlnk xrefid="f0403803">final assembly with its own model designation</hotlnk>. Refer to
                            the Model Designation Chart above.
                        </para>
                    </lev2>
